title: I FROM BRAZIL IM NEW PLAYER OCEANIA TRANSFER  BR>OCE  HELP MY!!
body: I'm new on the server I played on Brazilian Server oceania seemed odd wait until 30 minutes to start a match more okay I want to help someone please for me because I am link up and am very brass v lv 96

replies.body:
OCE has a much smaller server population than most, so queue times are longer, especially at unusual hours when most people are sleeping or working (2am-8am AEDT).

30 minutes is still unusual, though not unheard of. If you playing gamemode like ARAM or TT then queue times will of course be longer still.
